{"tid":2127321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"染髮女乘客疑在港鐵車廂公然小便 多名網民曾目擊：一程車不停轉位坐","createTime":"2020-07-27T09:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T09:39:12.000Z","uid":147522,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"816c94c36a14c2b91536c9d9582b9ea51b101996","tid":2127321,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"本港爆發第三波新冠肺炎疫情，近期新增確診個案更連續數日破百。在嚴峻疫情之下，大眾應該注意個人衛生。不過，近日就有網民分享自己乘搭港鐵時遇到的奇人奇事，指自己目擊一位女乘客在車廂公然小便。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在FB群組「將軍澳主場」分享圖片，指自己在乘搭港鐵時，見到一位染髮女乘客懷疑在車廂公然小便：「此女子地鐵痾尿 將軍澳人注意」，更透露尿液帶血，懷疑女子正值生理期。網民表示自己原意並非想公審該名女子：「唔係想公審佢....有機會係情緒有問題...但係呢啲非常時期...想叫大家小心啲...已經係第二次目擊」，又形容該位女乘客「由港島線到北角線再轉車坑口站落...佢仲要不斷轉位坐...」，呼籲大家在坐之前要望清楚座位的環境。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都留言表示自己曾遇見過該名女乘客，同樣發現她疑似在車廂痾尿，甚至「可以行行下就企响路中間痾，次次條裙都濕晒」。亦有人表示曾不幸中招：「差唔多到寶琳落車先發現原來勁大攤流咗去我企嗰個位」。香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良，曾指出冠狀病毒除了主要透過飛沫傳播，亦能夠通過尿液及糞便傳播，所以大家出門在外要留意周圍環境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VwjPM5P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwjPM5P.png&h=d072e537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36a43f69ed3ba0f8cab8db35284ed29618f60fd8","tid":2127321,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"與支那接軌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51019b2bdb11ab52e44e9c8eabf06e70388c3ad6","tid":2127321,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"看圖作文？"},{"pid":"1bda21d034d8e9d90c804ea394749b55971e606a","tid":2127321,"uid":334765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"黨鐵wfc"},{"pid":"5ef98260ef3835d910b1859ca4a6e16f9bf835f5","tid":2127321,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51019b2bdb11ab52e44e9c8eabf06e70388c3ad6","tid":2127321,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"看圖作文？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:11:00.000Z","msg":"留意白衫個個腳下面"},{"pid":"d13a8adf503abe4eadf4265a42cbd73fed70545b","tid":2127321,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"仲打咩格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effcf014fbee52a7d4cb52496d4b0f8cca3ec29b","tid":2127321,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"有無血尿圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01389230f8795b862468e15fefc312c3ac15c404","tid":2127321,"uid":270308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"露出的快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a479aade1f8045280750fb5de46d8c5b7ab73db0","tid":2127321,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"高清無碼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf56a51428048be2506bb183f2ba95818a44165","tid":2127321,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"佢屙果日嘅夜晚仲同男友一齊行sogo 大約8點左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸 親眼見到"},{"pid":"c6d117045b0f15b284ab94a1b8056b4262814ebf","tid":2127321,"uid":105133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"好似係尖沙咀見過佢"}]}